      "description": "This vehicle is in impeccable, showroom-quality condition, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains its original luster with no chips, scratches, or swirl marks, while the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear on the upholstery or dashboard. Mechanically, it performs flawlessly, with every feature and system functioning exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that presents and drives as if it were brand new.",
