    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited for whoever ends up with this beauty. It is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it garage-parked and sparkling clean. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and honestly feels brand new. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
