    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is an investment-grade E46 M3, preserved in concours-level condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a documented history of preventative rod bearing and VANOS solenoid service. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is structurally immaculate, featuring verified subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec suspension setup with fresh bushings and OEM dampers. Retaining all original VIN-matched panels and an oxidation-free undercarriage, this vehicle offers the tactile mechanical feedback and high-revving performance characteristic of a true analog masterpiece.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Original paint. No mechanical issues. Clean title. Garage kept.",
