    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true time-capsule vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The factory paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the leather is supple and matte with no bolster wear, the original floor mats are pristine, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment to the smallest backlight\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive, open-book service history using only genuine OEM parts. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion or road grime. It drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new car, offering a silent, powerful, and vibration-free experience. This is a collector-grade example that satisfies the most discerning eye.",
